  <!-- ABSTRACT -->
  <h2>Abstract</h2>
  <p>In the modern era, personal safety is a paramount concern, especially for children who are increasingly mobile and independent. ChildGuard is an innovative mobile application designed to provide parents with a robust, real-time safety net. By leveraging Flutter's cross-platform capabilities and Firebase's real-time synchronization, the app offers features like live GPS tracking, geofencing (Safe Zones), and a unique hardware-triggered SOS mechanism. A key highlight of this project is the integration of Roman Urdu documentation within the source code, making it an accessible educational resource for students in local regions. This document outlines the methodology, architecture, and technical implementation of ChildGuard.</p>

  <div class="page-break"></div>

