  <!-- 8. CONCLUSION -->
  <h2>8. Conclusion</h2>
  <p>The ChildGuard project successfully demonstrates the power of modern mobile frameworks in solving real-world safety challenges. By providing a seamless link between parents and children, the app reduces response times and enhances peace of mind. Future enhancements could include AI-based behavioral analysis and smart-watch integration for even faster SOS triggers.</p>

